{"tid":389162,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台證問題 (BNO)","createTime":"2017-09-06T04:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T06:14:29.000Z","uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99d54e17739b63d8562c8d7de33bf7b6b5880b14","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去台灣幾日<br />\n因為我以前去係用開特衰 過期之後就續番BNO 從未用過BNO入台灣境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦<br />\n1. 係整台證網站上面國藉我應該揀番香港? 因為佢網上寫跟護照 但護照寫BN (O)...<br />\n2. 我21-23去台灣一次 返黎香港一日 25又要再去 咁我係咪要整兩張台證?<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b49c52c0cb9e9e5567355f222d979becc31ba9","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759ff47a5fa857ba7166f7b8fb3bb14bdb16b574","tid":389162,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"用過特衰入境就要用返特衰，如果唔係會比人拒絕入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2）係"},{"pid":"a7ff13f9da4f0dfdcc3bdfc91ec25b9f7b886336","tid":389162,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"玩完 港澳用英葡護照入台係好煩"},{"pid":"f1db9888181e9ca1b7545b4cb4d39b5e45f86eaa","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用過特衰入境就要用返特衰，如果唔係會比人拒絕入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2）係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我已經無左本特衰啦喎 仲點用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f7ea3227d6cc52bbac92b7edba82d5b3f771ca","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci