b850c43fa04fb91b4d7142fc329.jpg&h=2d072a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fee54dd93c1ea7b895bea88aafb3d1954a090e9d","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台灣將 BNO 同 BC 分開<br />\nBNO 先用得入台證<br />\n國籍揀香港就得</blockquote><br />\n身份揀 &quot;香港居民&quot;</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂你阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5368e9a48755b3a856171b425c90749d458784ed","tid":389162,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"台灣法例入面<br />\nbno 同 特衰都係香港護照<br />\n唔存在兩本護照雙重國籍問題"},{"pid":"d11f28b17abcd737111c01e73fe300819acf0863","tid":389162,"uid":70801,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 揸住本BNO都唔影響你係港豬既身份<br />\n國籍都係中共"},{"pid":"b1d6529b45711bb5ff1d4337a70ee510ce0a3492","tid":389162,"uid":64582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"台灣眼中<br />\nBNO=特衰<br />\n所以無分別,如果你用BC就真係唔得啦"},{"pid":"99edf69e372f1b3fa6b28671be8275ed23136e51","tid":389162,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣眼中<br />\nBNO=特衰<br />\n所以無分別,如果你用BC就真係唔得啦</blockquote><br />\n咁就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab02859036a3a2e85654039b6bfbbbd3975a7d8","tid":389162,"uid":68986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"咪撚聽班傻仔鳩up<br />\n1）Bno係台證申請方面，係用返港澳居民個張form申請<br />\n<br />\n2）係要申請兩次 因為你係進行左入境出境程序"},{"pid":"c6a560d72f6b6abd811d815707dcb2e765da