r />\n所以無分別,如果你用BC就真係唔得啦</blockquote><br />\n咁就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左 一拍本護照見code同護照no 同之前入境唔同<br />\n佢得鳩閒理你bno bc定特衰<br />\n等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦</blockquote><br />\n你肯收皮未? <br />\n人地打埋去問, 你都仲要柒落去"},{"pid":"800212226bd9dea1788dc7704c767c5e382a7851","tid":389162,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用過特衰入境就要用返特衰，如果唔係會比人拒絕入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2）係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我已經無左本特衰啦喎 仲點用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗去 信我</blockquote><br />\nagree <br />\n利申同你一樣 試過<br />\n最後番即日香港"},{"pid":"e415d961aa873de76b4dd445c14cdc527916d1dc","tid":389162,"uid":43392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"搭單一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個case係去程會由香港入台灣訓一晚<br />\n之後出境直接去日本，幾日後由日本再返台灣，再訓一晚就返香港<br />\n咁我係咪要係香港申請定2個入台証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3e28361274d02748b271417d32002b8ca0b9f8","tid":389162,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個case係去程會由香港入台灣訓一晚<br />\n之後出境直接去日本，幾日後由日本再返台灣，再訓一晚就返香港<br />\n咁我係咪要係香港申請定2個入台証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 